<i>Shelby.</i>

31
00:02:41,429 --> 00:02:42,514
<i>Bendera kotak-kotak dikeluarkan.</i>

32
00:02:43,807 --> 00:02:45,600
<i>Para penonton berdiri.</i>

33
00:02:45,767 --> 00:02:46,684
<i>Shelby.</i>

34
