00:35:11,042 --> 00:35:13,044
Mobil Frank Collins dan Steve McQueen.

544
00:35:13,211 --> 00:35:15,379
Aku lupa soal McQueen.

545
00:35:18,341 --> 00:35:19,342
Pagi.

546
00:35:20,218 --> 00:35:21,135
Bisa kubantu?

547
00:35:22,428 --> 00:35:23,554
Carroll Shelby?

548
00:35:24,889 --> 00:35:25,807
Mungkin.

549
00:35:27,266 --> 00:35:29,685
Lee Iacocca, Ford Motor.

550
00:35:32,772 --> 00:35:34,440
Apa cerita kunci pas ini?

551
